    },
    {
      "start": 123.89,
      "end": 128.89,
      "text": "진짜 얼마나 완벽했으면 이런 평을 다 받게 되었을까요"
    },
    {
      "start": 128.89,
      "end": 135.07,
      "text": "However, with amazingly new technology, now we have a new version of it"
