      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 186.04,
      "end": 189.5,
      "text": "완전 급전개되는 그런 느낌이 있었단 말이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 189.5,
      "end": 192.64,
      "text": "Did you like think about your childhood when you did something bad"
